<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" version="2.0"><channel><title>界面快报</title><link>https://jiemian.com/</link><description>界面快报</description><docs>http://www.rssboard.org/rss-specification</docs><generator>python-feedgen</generator><image><url>https://res.jiemian.com/assets/wap/common/img/jm-new-logo.png</url><title>界面快报</title><link>https://jiemian.com/</link></image><lastBuildDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 22:30:02 +0800</lastBuildDate><pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 22:30:02 +0800</pubDate><item><title>我国持续推进湿地保护，全国湿地面积稳定保持在5635万公顷以上</title><link>https://www.jiemian.com/article/12305309.html</link><description><![CDATA[<div class="article-content"><p>国家林草局最新数据显示，党的十八大以来，累计实施湿地保护修复项目3700多个，新增和修复湿地100多万公顷，全国湿地面积稳定保持在5635万公顷以上。建立各类湿地自然保护地2200多处。（央视新闻）</p>
